  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3 re-classification)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. Following a regulatory query, the model risk level was re-classified to MRL 3 to reflect the high decision consequence and the absence of independent experimental replication. Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been assessed and meet or exceed required gradations. The 'Use error' factor was judged by the assessment team to be inapplicable to a purely computational workflow and therefore no assessment activities were conducted; the factor is carried as not-assessed in the package record.",
