    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been fully assessed and all meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 3. The 'Use error' factor has not been assessed; the team's position is that this factor does not apply to a controlled computational submission. On this basis the team accepts the credibility evidence as sufficient to support the regulatory decision, noting that the unassessed factor does not materially affect the hemolysis prediction confidence given the controlled simulation environment.",
